Let $M$ be a generalized Cohen-Macaulay module over $(R,{\frak{m}},k)$ such that $d=\dim M>0$ and let ${\frak{q}}=(x_1,\ldots, x_d)$ be a parameter ideal of $M$. Then the following statements are equivalent.

