\label{characterization}
Let $(R,{\frak{m}},k)$ be a local ring of characteristic $p>0$ and of dimension $d>0$. Then $R$ is $F$-injective if and only if for some (and hence any) filter regular sequence $x_1,\ldots,x_d$, we have

