@V\overline{F}VV @V\overline{F}VV @V\overline{F}VV  (\star \star)\\
R/(\underline{x}^{[p]})^{\lim} @>>> R/(\underline{x}^{[2p]})^{\lim} @>>> R/(\underline{x}^{[3p]})^{\lim} @>>> \cdots
